{"tid":1059260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★World No IT】Gmail及Google Drive疑全球大死機","createTime":"2019-03-13T04:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T07:49:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b3af74bf4123ec0cf66067e4769d51ccda079b22","tid":1059260,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190313/photo/bkn-20190313113904609-0313_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190313120720\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190313%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190313113904609-0313_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190313120720&h=2d5f7c08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGmail及Google Drive服務在周二至周三（12至13日）疑發生大規模故障，有用戶投訴，使用Gmail沒法加上附件，或沒法傳送有附件的電郵。Google接到用戶回報問題後，就事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n除了Gmail，Google雲端硬碟也同時出現故障，根據監察網站downdetector與Google旗下G Suite資料，全球多個地區同時出現問題。<br />\n<br />\n《G Suite 狀態資訊主頁》中，可看Gmail、雲端硬碟亮起橙色，內文寫著「Google已經着手處理故障」。目前故障原因不明，Google未有正式回應。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190313/bkn-20190313113904609-0313_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190313%2Fbkn-20190313113904609-0313_00822_001.html&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=06b4320c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190313/bkn-20190313113904609-0313_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4e07b93f79e8fabc64eb53fb394c2d78a4e2d654","tid":1059260,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"目前故障原因不明，Google未有正式回應。<br />\n目前故障原因不明，Google未有正式回應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nnone fix<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29e7a2fb6f2f994482fb80370148ddf27ed7c8a","tid":1059260,"uid":137096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e07b93f79e8fabc64eb53fb394c2d78a4e2d654","tid":1059260,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite